WEBVTT

00:11:29.235 --> 00:11:31.624
and manipulation of the family court system

00:11:31.624 --> 00:11:34.447
to terrify the victim and her children,

00:11:34.447 --> 00:11:39.373
who are regularly forced by family court judges

00:11:39.373 --> 00:11:41.342
to spend unsupervised time

00:11:41.342 --> 00:11:45.013
with the man who beat their mother.

00:11:45.013 --> 00:11:49.188
And still we ask, why doesn't she just leave?

00:11:49.188 --> 00:11:50.942
I was able to leave,

00:11:50.942 --> 00:11:53.844
because of one final, sadistic beating

00:11:53.844 --> 00:11:57.003
that broke through my denial.

00:11:57.003 --> 00:12:00.173
I realized that the man who I loved so much